<h2>Transitions</h2>
<p>Transitions are used to change one or more css property from one value to another. Although they can be triggered multiple times, they are not intended to be run in a loop. Unlike animations (that use the css <code>animation</code> property), transitions cannot use keyframes and are thus limited in their ability to coordinate different timing for different properties.</p>

